\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did your father have people he worked with coming to visit him?
