\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Perhaps your mother had people from other parts of the village coming to visit her, can you remember that happening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you remember what sort of things these people did, what their jobs were or what they did when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 I don't know they did anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Would they sit and chat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did your mother ever give them anything to drink when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Not - no beer or nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Perhaps tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Or anything to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 What sort of things would she give them to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well - cakes and - bread and butter and all like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you think that your parents shared the same friends? Or did they have friends of their own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Money was the main problem then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 You don't remember your mother having any friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Oh they were - at Redruth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you think she felt isolated by living down here?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No, she - I don't think so. Her father was a - captain of a mine at - at Redruth. He got killed - in the mine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 When she was young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did she remember him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 My mother did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 But you never met him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Were friends ever invited to the home for something special, for a special occasion perhaps, like an anniversary or a birthday or somet
hing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 I don't remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you think they might have been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Might have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you remember friends calling in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Was there a lot of coming and going at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends, in the way of amusement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Oh - talking, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did they play cards or any sort of games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 I don't remember, no. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you think they ever went on outings together for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well not very far like you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time before 1918 d
id you think of some people belonging to one group and some people belonging to another group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did you think of people being worse off than yourself or better off than yourself in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 We were all - all the same then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 This was in Newleyn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Why was that? What do you mean they were all the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well - did - didn't look up to anyone like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Nobody at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Was there anyone that you'd call sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 How would you approach a clergyman or a doctor or someone like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Oh say - say sir - sir - to him wouldn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 What sort of social group would you think you yourself belonged to in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 The middle class I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 What sort of people belonged to the same group as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 I was known by everybody here you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 You think everyone was the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another sort?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No. I wasn't brought up to - that way at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Were you ever taught to touch your cap to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 As a gesture of respect when you passed them in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Only a woman you knew or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Oh everybody was alike then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 In Newlyn in those days who do you remember would be thought of as the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well - they were - I suppose - the best then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 This was the Bohlhos?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Who were what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well they were bankers. Big bankers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did they live locally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did they have a lot to do with how things worked and how life carried on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well he was the Chairman of the - Harbourmasters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 So he'd be an important man among the fishermen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did you ever meet the Bohlhos?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Socially?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Would they be considered important because they were bankers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well - I don't think - I don't think he did any - any harm to anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Good natured?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 
Did you come into contact shopkeepers or members of the church, clergy, and teachers, do you remember who they associated with? Would you remember teachers visiting home? What sort of people wo
uld you say went to church in those days and what sort of people went to chapel, was there a difference between them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well yes. Yes, it was a difference.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you think that all the people in Newlyn had the same standard of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Would you say there were different groups at all, different standards of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you remember everybody's house being clean for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Everybody having enough to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you remember a time perhaps when the people next door didn't have as much to eat or to spend as your family did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you remember some families being thought of as rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 What about other families being thought of as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes, well - everybody was - respectable then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 You didn't have any rough families at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No. Not -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Not people who parents thought weren't worth knowing, do you remember that?
