Do you remember your mother and father having the same attitude to people in different classes, would your mother be as respectful to the minister as your father would be? Or did they behave differently to different people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No, I think they were - they looked up to the - the minister and all like that.
