\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 What about the Bolithos.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 You thought of them as that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Do you know what you meant by it if you called them that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 He - Bolithos, he was a - well a landowner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Would you think that gentlemen were landowners then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
