\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did you like him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 When you were naughty did your mother ever say she'd call the policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid266305 ST  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Well she might have said it.
