\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8718733 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15535941\charrsid6832661 Did he ask for his money regularly?
